      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> steak[s]</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it adjust to room temperature</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into thin wedges</p>",
