    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your<strong> pork loin steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Season both sides with <strong>salt</strong> and sprinkle with<strong> half</strong> your <strong>smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>coated steak[s]</strong></p>",
