    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated steak[s] </strong>and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until browned and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? Use 2 pans!</p><p>Once cooked, transfer the <strong>cooked steak[s]</strong> to a clean chopping board, cover with a clean tea towel and leave to rest for 2 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1725535580160-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1725535580160-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1725535580160-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1725535580160-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1725535580160-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the steak[s] are cooking, heat a pot with a lid with a small drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>onion wedges</strong> with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for an initial 2-3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1725535585637-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1725535585637-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
